HEADWORD: Free-martin
<hw>Free"-mar`tin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An imperfect female calf, twinborn with a male, which is sterile as
a result of exposure to masculinizing hormones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Freemason</ent>⟦br⟧
